    <summary>Specifies the border styles for a form.</summary>
    <remarks>
      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 This enumeration is used by the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form> class. It represents the different styles of the form. The default style is `Sizable`.  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 In this example, you change the form border style to `Fixed3d` and display the border's information using a label. This example assumes that you have already created a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Form> named `Form1`.  
  
